PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument (DESIGNATION AND REVOCATION OF SURRENDERS) wherein the ESQUIMALT BAND OF INDIANS (a) surrenders, for a term of 99 years, approximately 8.64 hectares of Esquimalt Indian Reserve No. 0 in British Columbia, for the purpose of leasing it to Kosapsum Development Corporation, and (b) revokes a number of previous designations.
